---
layout: post
title: "Blogging in Malayalam using Wordpress"
date: 2013-02-14 11:15
comments: true
categories: [malayalam,wordpress,blogging,language]
---
To write blogs in malayalam, you can use the Google *transliteration* service.After that you can copy the content and paste it to the wordpress editor.

To read your malayalam blogs, you have to edit *wp-config.php*, which will be present in the root directory of the web hosting server, where you had installed the wordpress.
Look for the following line :

`define(‘DB_CHARSET’, ‘utf8′);`

Comment the above line :

`//define(‘DB_CHARSET’, ‘utf8′);`

Save the file in the server and publish your blog.Now everyone can read your malayalam blogs.

Check below :-

